  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting of the development of public service media in Algeria.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will focus on supporting staff in implementing PSB values including through the production of programming that gives a voice to all Algerian citizens at Radio Algeria. It also aims to support Radio Algeria in drafting Editorial Guidelines they have ownership of, and which are relevant to the Algerian context, in consultation with their staff. The project will ensure sustainability post-project by working with Radio Algeria&apos;s in-house trainers, trained under previous projects and HR department to develop durable training material and resources which can be used across the organisation. The success of BBC Media Action&apos;s partnership with Radio Algeria has triggered the interest of ENTV and APS which the project will also include.</narrative>
  </description>
